room_title: Escape room "Sundown Saloon" by Portland Escape Rooms in Portland
room_address: 10700 SW Beaverton-Hillsdale Hwy, Suite 118 Beaverton OR 97005
room_description: A quiet night turns dire when the Blue Bandit and his gang of outlaws hold up the Sundown Saloon!  In this Wild West adventure, you and your fellow cowpokes have to get word to the Sheriff... before the Sundown Saloon burns to the ground!
